metadata.name: A Mouse Full Of Joy
metadata.description:
Experience the magic of Disney with this colourful creation by Tim Rogerson, which has been created to commemorate the 90th anniversary of Mickey Mouse’s film debut.

Depicting Walt Disney’s popular character in a Cubist style and Basquiat colour scheme, the remarqued edition features a miniature hand-drawn pen sketch of Mickey Mouse and is accompanied by a certificate bearing the official Disney Fine Art logo.
